### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api
@authToken = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Inscription (Register) - Membre par défaut
# @name registerMembre
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jean Membre",
  "email": "jean.membre@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 3. Inscription (Register) - Organisateur
# @name registerOrg
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Org",
  "email": "alce.org@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "ORGANISATEUR"
}

###

### 4. Connexion (Login)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice.org@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 5. Récupérer mon profil (Me) - Nécessite d'avoir lancé Login avant
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJjbW9ycHg2bjMwMDAxZDE2d2EzbHcxY3hkIiwiZW1haWwiOiJhbGljZS5vcmdAZXhhbXBsZS5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiT1JHQU5JU0FURVVSIiwic3RhdHVzIjoiQUNUSVZFIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc3OTMwNTExLCJleHAiOjE3Nzg1MzUzMTF9.8OgypEiQ6wbGRIfctMi3Ts3FZpKs6hO7sJzsN9XjF9g
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 6. Mettre à jour mon profil
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJjbW9ycHg2bjMwMDAxZDE2d2EzbHcxY3hkIiwiZW1haWwiOiJhbGljZS5vcmdAZXhhbXBsZS5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiT1JHQU5JU0FURVVSIiwic3RhdHVzIjoiQUNUSVZFIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc3OTMwNTExLCJleHAiOjE3Nzg1MzUzMTF9.8OgypEiQ6wbGRIfctMi3Ts3FZpKs6hO7sJzsN9XjF9g
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Organimatrice"
}

###

### 7. Créer un Cercle (Organisateur requis)
# @name createCircle
POST {{baseUrl}}/circles
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJjbW9ycTVkdm0wMDAweWJ5bmxneXdzMG54IiwiZW1haWwiOiJhbGNlLm9yZ0BleGFtcGxlLmNvbSIsInJvbGUiOiJPUkdBTklTQVRFVVIiLCJzdGF0dXMiOiJBQ1RJVkUiLCJpYXQiOjE3Nzc5MzA4OTQsImV4cCI6MTc3ODUzNTY5NH0.tsMdiF4kuAgqOwejqRlQTubDZY5ySkXynumFP6rh5ng
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tontine Solidarité 2026",
  "description": "Cercle pour l'épargne projet immobilier",
  "amount": 50000,
  "frequency": "MONTHLY",
  "maxMembers": 10,
  "isPublic": true
}

###

### 8. Lister les Cercles Publics
GET {{baseUrl}}/circles
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 9. Voir les détails d'un Cercle
@circleId = {{createCircle.response.body.id}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/circles/{{circleId}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 10. Rechercher un cercle par un Membre (Jean)
# @name loginMembre
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jean.membre@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 11. Rejoindre un Cercle (Membre)
@tokenMembre = {{loginMembre.response.body.token}}
POST {{baseUrl}}/circles/{{circleId}}/join
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenMembre}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 12. Créer une Invitation (Alice Org)
# @name createInvitation
POST {{baseUrl}}/circles/{{circleId}}/invitations
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "invite@example.com",
  "expiresInDays": 5
}

###

### 13. Accepter une Invitation (Jean Membre)
@inviteToken = {{createInvitation.response.body.token}}
POST {{baseUrl}}/invitations/{{inviteToken}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenMembre}}
Content-Type: application/json
